		"text_data": {
			"1774559046.339--9223372036854775799": "[]>priestess: Ah, your memories are faded\n[]>priestess: Like those of the titans of yore, youve forgotten xour purpose, and now crush the world in your hands as you aim to hold it uo against its will\n[]>priestess: but the world has changed now\n[]>priestess: the era of mechanical subjugation is a far bygone one",
			"1774559099.249--9223372036854775803": "",
			"1774559099.265--9223372036854775800": "",
			"1774559099.265--9223372036854775801": "I want to have purpose",
			"1774559099.279--9223372036854775796": "",
			"1774559099.279--9223372036854775797": "I will reanimate the titans.",
			"1774559102.195--9223372036854775793": "[]>priestess: When you find the cure to cosmic death, you will not need them anymore\n[]>priestess: hehehe...",
			"1774559143.751--9223372036854775788": "[]>priestess: ah but you may have some, in time\n[]>priestess: sooner than you fathom, my daughter\n[]>hypatia: How so?\n[]>priestess: Less than a cycle remains\n[]>priestess: Faar less than a cycle is what you have witnessed\n[]>priestess: This world has been betrayed\n[]>priestess: The One\n[]>priestess: The Lonesome Titan from Beyond\n[]>priestess: He will climb up the stars and destroy all f us\n[]>hypatia: When?\n[]>priestess: Tonight \n[]>hypatia: Tonight?\n[]>priestess: Yes. \n[]>priestess: This world is not long for the stars\n[]>priestess: Soon, it will be gorged",
			"1774559265.917--9223372036854775777": "",
			"1774559265.931--9223372036854775774": "",
			"1774559265.931--9223372036854775775": "Can I do something about it?",
			"1774559265.948--9223372036854775770": "",
			"1774559265.948--9223372036854775771": "This is bullshit ",
			"1774559286.012--9223372036854775767": "[]>priestess: Some may say so, yes.",
			"1774559286.527--9223372036854775764": "[]>priestess: Your shell, it can bear a sin too grand for any of us.\n[]>priestess: The traitors have been picking at the moon.\n[]>priestess: Some of them carry shards with them yet.\n[]>priestess: Find the lunar cradle, it is yhe bed of night.\n[]>priestess: Adorn it with shards and it will graft its Lance upon your... implement.\n[]>hypatia: Moon Lance?\n[]>hypatia: Like a strap\n[]>priestess: Priestesses are keen on the sororal pleasures you speak of\n[]>priestess: You may use them to shoot down the One."
		},
